-- Bain's Edcon Says Its Second-Quarter Adjusted Earnings Increased by 28%
-- B y   V e r n o n   W e s s e l s
-- 2010-11-23T07:08:44Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-23/bain-s-edcon-says-its-second-quarter-adjusted-earnings-increased-by-28-.html
Edcon Holdings Ltd., a South African
retailer owned by Bain Capital LLC, said second-quarter adjusted
earnings before interest, tax, depreciation and amortization
increased by 28 percent to 490 million rand.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
